title: Dakine Tanner Hall Team Mission Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Tanner Hall Team Mission Pack.
Mission Features:
- Vertical board carry straps
- Fleece lined goggle pocket
- Padded laptop sleeve
- Fits most 15" laptops
- Organizer pocket
- Fleece lined sunglass pocket
- Padded waist belt
